                         The No Enemies POKE seems to render the game pointless!

                         The Use Interface 1 POKE seems useless with an Emulator!

                         The "Stop Colourcode" seems similarily useless, not to
                         mention it promotes piracy on the Spectrum! (Ahem)

                         And I don't know WHICH bugs are fixed, but I assume
                         they can only help!

                         Rastan.
